examples.en: The job requires someone who is good at multitasking.
Women seem to be able to multitask better than men.
Sometimes they try to multitask and again end up doing nothing
Young people who multitask while driving slow their reaction time.
When you're working under pressure, it's important to be able to multitask and prioritize.
Saying that a netbook can't multitask is like saying a compact car can't carry passengers.
